Evaluations encourage students to place total responsibility for the quality of their education on their teachers.
Students should have the right to criticize both content and the methods of teaching. On one hand, the students may become more focused and engage. In addition students become more carefully to listen during the class. On the other hand they can develop criticism skill.
However, evaluating teachers can effect on teachers too, they can improve themselves and they can enhance their way, method and behavior.
At the end, evaluating teachers are good idea to make students decide and control their education to let them feel better.